                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260622-21-off91 t18260622-21-crimeloc94"></join>. On the 8th of June, from information I received I went out, and saw the prisoner in St. Andrew's-court, with a crowd round her; Watson had her in custody, and produced this piece of muslin to me, which had been stolen from between our outer and inner doors.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260622-21-person221">
                  WILLIAM 
                  THOMAS WATSON
